81
00:03:26,930 --> 00:03:30,420
The CEO of Google’s parent company, Alphabet,

82
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:34,880
was asked to testify before the US House Judiciary
Committee on Tuesday.

83
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,640
There were a lot of issues on the table,

84
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:39,390
but a key one was how Google has been accused
of

85
00:03:39,390 --> 00:03:44,030
secretly working on a censored search app
for the Chinese market.

86
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:48,520
Internally, Google gave it the codename Project
Dragonfly.

87
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:51,020
But the CEO stuck pretty closely to the talking
points

88
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:53,650
Google has been using since these accusations

89
00:03:53,650 --> 00:03:54,990
