90
00:03:54,990 --> 00:03:57,690
"Right now, we have no plans to launch in
China.

91
00:03:57,690 --> 00:04:01,210
We don't have a search product there.

92
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:04,930
Our core mission is to provide users access
to information,

93
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:07,880
