launch it?

102
00:04:29,910 --> 00:04:32,620
Now Amnesty International, Human Rights Watch,

103
00:04:32,620 --> 00:04:34,220
and the Committee to Protect Journalists

104
00:04:34,220 --> 00:04:38,340
